Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.46,0:00:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, it seems so unfair that I got to spend so\Nmuch time with James and Lilly and you so little.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.12,0:00:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Harry. -- Can we really trust Sirius Black?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.02,0:00:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what about that daily prophet article,\Nwhere YOU went on the record saying...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.21,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...you want to find Harry and you want to drug and kill him!\N- That's a lie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was magically misquoted by that dumbass Rita Skeeter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.53,0:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What I  actually said was: ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.83,0:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...I want to hug and kiss him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.76,0:00:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe him, guys. He saw my\Nparents in the mirror and, well, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...you can't fake that.\N- No, you can't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.45,0:00:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing here, Sirius?\N- Yeah, I mean if you don't want to kill Harry,\Nthen what's the point of coming to Hogwarts at all?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.76,0:00:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was rotting away in my\Nprison cell in Azkaban, I ah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.05,0:00:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...received a package. And attached to it was this note.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It reads:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.23,0:01:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Sirius Black, inclused is a tool that you can\Nuse to escape Azkaban and sneak into Hogwarts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.14,0:01:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry! Harry Potter is in grave danger!\NSigned: Little d.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.81,0:01:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Little d?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Little Dumbledore!\N- My thoughts exactly!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.09,0:01:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nice to know that the old man still believed in me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.29,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I opened the package and inside I found this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.53,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fathers old invisibility cloak.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.54,0:01:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha, we used to use it to play jokes on Snape!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And we went solve mysteries and shit, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.21,0:01:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...here. Your dad wanted you to have\Nthis -- when you're old enough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.86,0:01:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thanks. Hey Ron, am I invisible?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sirius, I don't think I'm in any kind of grave danger.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.87,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Harry! Jesus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.35,0:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looked like you were in danger\Nduring that quidditch match.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good thing my package made it to you on time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You really put it to good use.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.47,0:02:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You sent that firebolt!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.88,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- I sure did.\N- Harry! Harry, on the map!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Get under the cloak! If you guys are seen\Nhelping me you'll all be in really big trouble!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no! But if they find you\Nthey're gonna send you back to Azkaban!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.17,0:02:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It was all worth it as long as you know the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now quick! Get under the cloak!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- No. no!\N- Alohomora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the devil is going on heeeere?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.04,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies! You can't do nothing!\NYou must be here for something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Or for someONE!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.46,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the penalty is for aiding a fugitive?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you all expelled!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- But we weren't doing anything!\N- Shut up, Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arrogance is insufferable\Njust like your dead-beat father.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And like him it's going to get you killed!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.21,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, until I find Black, I'm going\Nto make your life miserable.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll wish you WERE expelled!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them alone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You -- butt trumpet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.57,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sirius is doing the butt-trumpet]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, but this isn't anything like it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[More butt-trumpet]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Expelliarmus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha. Sirius Black!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping I'd be the one to find you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, you did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- So leave the kids out of this.\N- He's innocent!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the judge of that, Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.86,0:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Through all these years, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're still a no-good weinerjacket!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.50,0:03:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't stand that she picked James -- over yer!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a reason! Give me a reason, I swear I'll do it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.22,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wish Dumbledore were here!\N- I am here, Night Troll!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so am I!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius Black!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've been looking for you a long time!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke into the castle using this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is Potter doing here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing important. I believe Black\Nhas confounded the children.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I think maybe you're the one\Nthat's been confounded, Snape!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the name on the tag! Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.17,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were guilty from the moment\NI layed my eyes on you three little turds!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.63,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you and your loser friends\Nare gonna come with me to Azkaban!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.77,0:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! It's impossible!\NHarry didn't help Sirius break in, because...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.54,0:04:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmaster, how could you let\Nthis criminal into the castle?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in THAT outfit...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarfy, my reasons are my own.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is just -- too -- good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.08,0:04:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I was gonna destroy you, Dumbledore.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're dead!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Unless...\N- Unless what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I make you a deal, Dumbledore.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can either kiss the dementors...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...or you can kiss -- Umbridge!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[No-cryings from nearly everybody]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worth it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose neither!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Snape it's time to show where your true loyalty lies!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the children for me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, -- looks like we're out -- again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Disaparate!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, magic!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?! Where d'he go???
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He disaparated!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bullshit, Snape! You can't disaparate\Ninside of Hogwarts, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You got lucky, Potter! But I know you're guilty too!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna get all of you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.11,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because with Dumbledore gone -- guess\Nwho gets to be the headmaster now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me?\N- Snape?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.37,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Me! Your mama! Umbridge!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.47,0:05:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And from now on we're gonna be\Ndoing things around here MY WAY!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.17,0:06:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be doing things\NTHE UMBRIDGE WAY!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[-- End of Act 1 --]
